<!DOCTYPE codename-engine-dialogue>
<dialogue box="dialogueBox">

    <char name="megablade" char="megablade" position="left" defaultAnim="look"/>
    <char name="bf-xmas" char="bf-xmas" position="right" defaultAnim="smile"/>
    <char name="pico-xmas" char="pico-xmas" position="right" defaultAnim="questioning"/>
    <char name="pico-xmas-left" char="pico-xmas-left" position="left" defaultAnim="bored"/>
    <char name="father-xmas" char="grace-picnic" position="left" defaultAnim="smile"/>
    <char name="mother-xmas" char="grace-picnic" position="left" defaultAnim="grin"/>

    
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="look" changeMusic="dio/music/christmas" musicVolume="0.8">
        Despite being battered and bruised, Pico and Benjamin manage to escape Mairest.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="closedtalk">
        While healing, a treacherous month flies by, which together they spend resting and tending to wounds.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="smile">
        Soon after, the boys felt well and brave enough to face the streets once again.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="look">
        Signs of the holiday season litter the scene, with snowflakes dancing in the air, golden bells ringing, and children laughing.
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="talk">
        A crowd of strangers whisper to one another in excitement, waiting beside a sign that reads: “Annual Holiday Fairest Meet and Greet!”
    </line>
    <line char="megablade" changeDefAnim="closedsmile">
        The two boys enjoy the winter season with smiles, distracted by one another’s company
    </line>

    
    <line char="pico-xmas-left" changeDefAnim="bored" changeMusic="dio/music/merrymaking" musicVolume="0.6">
        I can't believe you're actually making me wear this.
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="smile">
        Why? You look adorable.
    </line>
    <line char="pico-xmas-left" changeDefAnim="bored">
        I know, that's the problem.
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="happy">
        Come on Toughie, this is our first time out and about in a month. At least try to enjoy it-
    </line>

    
    <line char="">
        THERE THEY ARE!
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="scared">
        Huh?!
    </line>
    <line char="pico-xmas" changeDefAnim="questioning">
        A crowd...?
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="PLEASEWORK">
        ...Shit, what day is it?
    </line>
    <line char="pico-xmas" changeDefAnim="questioning">
        The 17th... why?
    </line>
    <line char="mother-xmas" changeDefAnim="grin">
        OUR SON!
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="what">
        ...that’s why.
    </line>

    
    <line char="father-xmas" changeDefAnim="smile">
        Just in time for the holidays!
    </line>
    <line char="mother-xmas" changeDefAnim="condescending">
        We were beginning to fear the worst...
    </line>
    <line char="bf-xmas" changeDefAnim="what">
        ...
    </line>
    <line char="father-xmas" changeDefAnim="happy">
        How about we celebrate, sport?
    </line>
    <line char="mother-xmas" changeDefAnim="grin">
        Aaaaaaand finally get you home!
    </line>
    

</dialogue>
